data.description: Luxury Estate in Lake Heather's beautiful gated lake community. This gorgeous 7 bedroom estate on the water has it all! Enter into the 2 story foyer with a beautiful chandelier and outstanding staircase leading up to the 2nd floor of the home. The study or office is just off the foyer with a fireplace and magnificent built-in book cases. The master bedroom and bath are on the main level. Another fireplace is located between the kitchen and dining room which has soaring ceilings. The basement has another total living area with a kitchen, dinning room, laundry, den, two bedrooms, full bath, sitting room, full bar and patio over looking the water. There are two  2 car garages, one on the main level and one on the basement level. There is an elevator, 5 A/C units, 2 gas hot water heaters, and a full house vacuum.This home has all the custom finishes, crown molding, plantation shutters, and so much more including a well manicured lawn, and double driveways. Priced to sell!
